    "statement": "**Agents Towards Production** is your hands-on guide to every building block of a GenAI agent stack.  \nAll knowledge is delivered through runnable tutorials covering orchestration, memory, observability, deployment, security, and more. Each tutorial lives in its own folder with ready-to-run notebooks or code files, so you can move from concept to working agent in minutes.",
